body_html: I am seeing this on large dataset too - and it is repeatable. Tried clearing up my cache and reboots, also tweaking around parallel_interleave(cycle_length), num_parallel_calls and buffer_size of my shuffle_and_repeat. - Everything's like a temporary fix but the underlying problem is still there.
